body_html:
I'm not familiar with tensorflow_transform but if it produces a TF graph that XLA can compile then it should be okay to use it with tfcompile. tfcompile compiles a TF graph to machine code via XLA; so any TF graph that XLA supports is fine as input, it doesn't matter whether the TF graph was produced via tensorflow_transform or some other means.

Perhaps you could try compiling a graph produced by tensorflow_transform using tfcompile?
